dc_title_s: Archived Land Use Land Cover 2002: Maryland
dc_description_s: This is a MD iMAP hosted service. Find more information on http://imap.maryland.gov. This layer contains land use land cover information for the year 2002. The Land Use Cover map and data is used to show development trends on the landscape in Maryland. The Maryland Department of Planning (MDP) created the first Land Use/Land Cover map in 1973 and updated it in 2002 and 2010. For more information see http://www. mdp. state. md. us/OurWork/landuse. shtmlMap Service Link: http://archive. geodata. md. gov/imap/rest/services/PlanningCadastre/MD_ArchivedLandUseLandCover/MapServer/1
